--Abstraction: Process of hiding complex information
Encapsulation: Process of protecting internal workings.

--Abstraction: Implemented by using 'abstract' keyword hence it is abstract class
Encapsulation: Implemented by using access specifier like private, protected and public hence it will have concrete classes.

--Abstraction: It can be accessed using method overriding in derived classes
Encapsulation: It can be accessed using getter, setter method
